Directions for BBQ Spice Rub: Combine Spice Rub BBQ ingredients in a jar with a lid. Makes 2/3 cup spice rub mix. Directions for Shreddies Snack Mix: Combine Shreddies, crackers, and peanuts in large bowl. Melt butter; stir in oil, and BBQ Spice Rub; drizzle over cereal mixture and mix. Spread evenly on parchment paper lined baking sheet. Bake at 250 degrees F for 30 min., stirring every 10 min. Cool.